[
    {
        "content": "<p>alexcrichton opened <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13330\">PR #13330</a> from <code>alexcrichton:fix-exnref-ownership</code> to <code>bytecodealliance:main</code>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><code>set_pending_exception</code> didn't have a write barrier to handle any<br>\n  previously configured exception.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>When an <code>exnref</code> was caught it didn't go through <code>expose_gc_ref_to_wasm</code>.</p>\n</li>\n<li>During <code>throw_impl</code> the <code>exnref</code> wasn't cloned to give a strong<br>\n  reference to the store.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>All of these should now be fixed with some minor refactorings and such<br>\nto ensure we've got the right barriers in the right places.</p>\n<p>Closes <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/13316\">https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/13316</a></p>\n</blockquote>",
        "id": 593878023,
        "sender_full_name": "Wasmtime GitHub notifications bot",
        "timestamp": 1778272673
    },
