    {
        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"memo\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f4dd\" role=\"img\" title=\"memo\">:memo:</span> alexcrichton submitted <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13330#pullrequestreview-4275809348\">PR review</a>.</p>",
        "id": 594669614,
        "sender_full_name": "Wasmtime GitHub notifications bot",
        "timestamp": 1778616554
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"speech balloon\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f4ac\" role=\"img\" title=\"speech balloon\">:speech_balloon:</span> alexcrichton created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13330#discussion_r3229451454\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>The main reason was <code>gc_store.write_gc_ref(&amp;mut self.pending_exception, Some(exnref))</code> where it was easier to change this than to add a full matrix of helpers for <code>VMExnRef</code> for this one call. How strongly do you feel this should remain <code>VMExnRef</code>?</p>\n</blockquote>",
