    {
        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"memo\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f4dd\" role=\"img\" title=\"memo\">:memo:</span> fitzgen submitted <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13330#pullrequestreview-4276616144\">PR review</a>.</p>",
        "id": 594691704,
        "sender_full_name": "Wasmtime GitHub notifications bot",
        "timestamp": 1778624002
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"speech balloon\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f4ac\" role=\"img\" title=\"speech balloon\">:speech_balloon:</span> fitzgen created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13330#discussion_r3230170443\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Do we not already have <code>as_gc_ref[_mut]</code> helpers for <code>VMExnRef</code> like we do for <code>VM{Struct,Array,...}Ref</code>? Then we probably should, and they should each just be one liners</p>\n</blockquote>",
